# Living the gospel brings me joy

## 4 Nephi 1:15

> And it came to pass that there
> was no contention in the land,
> because of the love of God which did
> dwell in the hearts of the people.

## Question

<center>
<img src="happy_kids.jpg" width="600"/>
</center>

What commandments can we obey that will
make us happier?

* Read the scriptures
* Saying your prayers
* Being a good example
* Listen to mom and dad
  - Cleaning: it's boring, but you get to find your stuff
  - Rice and beans: makes you big and strong, be alive more times,
    boring for Leah


